            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EPhilip%20preached%20the%20Word%2C%20and%20God%20performed%20miracles.%20The%20manifested%20presence%20of%20God%20brought%20joy%2C%20and%20the%20miracles%20attested%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20God%20was%20in%20Samaria.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%201%20Kings%208%3A11%2C%20God's%20presence%20so%20permeated%20the%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20magnificent%20temple%20that%20%22the%20priests%20could%20not%20continue%20their%20work%20because%20the%20glorious%20presence%20of%20the%20Lord%20filled%20the%20Temple.%22%20After%20the%20celebration%20of%20the%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%20that%20followed%20the%20dedication%20of%20Solomon's%20temple%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Jerusalem%20were%20%22joyful%20and%20happy%20because%20the%20Lord%20had%20been%20good%20to%20his%20servant%20David%20and%20to%20his%20people%20Israel%22%20(1%20Kings%208%3A66).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhen%20we%2C%20as%20believers%2C%20become%20dry%20and%20lethargic%20in%20our%20worship%20and%20evangelism%2C%20our%20real%20need%20is%20for%20more%20of%20the%20manifested%20presence%20of%20God.%20His%20presence%20refreshes%2C%20rejoices%2C%20renews%2C%20and%20makes%20us%20desire%20to%20tell%20everyone%20of%20His%20goodness.%20As%20Solomon%20did%2C%20let%20us%20fall%20to%20our%20knees%20and%20pray%20for%20His%20presence%20to%20fill%20our%20temples.%20Then%20all%20men%20will%20see%20and%20believe%20that%20%22there%20is%20no%20God%20like%20%5Bours%5D%20in%20all%20heaven%20or%20earth%22%20(1%20Kings%208%3A23).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Kings.8:1-66",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%208%3A1-66%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Ark%20Brought%20to%20the%20Temple%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3ESolomon%20then%20summoned%20to%20Jerusalem%20the%20elders%20of%20Israel%20and%20all%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20tribes%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20leaders%20of%20the%20ancestral%20families%20of%20the%20Israelites.%20They%20were%20to%20bring%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20to%20the%20Temple%20from%20its%20location%20in%20the%20City%20of%20David%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Zion.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20all%20the%20men%20of%20Israel%20assembled%20before%20King%20Solomon%20at%20the%20annual%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%2C%20which%20is%20held%20in%20early%20autumn%20in%20the%20month%20of%20Ethanim.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eat%20the%20festival%20in%20the%20month%20Ethanim%2C%20which%20is%20the%20seventh%20month.%3C%2Fem%3E%20The%20Festival%20of%20Shelters%20began%20on%20the%20fifteenth%20day%20of%20the%20seventh%20month%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20day%20occurred%20in%20late%20September%2C%20October%2C%20or%20early%20November.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20all%20the%20elders%20of%20Israel%20arrived%2C%20the%20priests%20picked%20up%20the%20Ark.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20priests%20and%20Levites%20brought%20up%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20along%20with%20the%20special%20tent%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Tent%20of%20Meeting%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20i.e.%2C%20the%20tent%20mentioned%20in%202%26%23xA0%3BSam%206%3A17%20and%201%26%23xA0%3BChr%2016%3A1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20all%20the%20sacred%20items%20that%20had%20been%20in%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%2C%20before%20the%20Ark%2C%20King%20Solomon%20and%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Israel%20sacrificed%20so%20many%20sheep%2C%20goats%2C%20and%20cattle%20that%20no%20one%20could%20keep%20count!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20priests%20carried%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20into%20the%20inner%20sanctuary%20of%20the%20Temple%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20Most%20Holy%20Place%26%23x2014%3Band%20placed%20it%20beneath%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20cherubim.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20cherubim%20spread%20their%20wings%20over%20the%20Ark%2C%20forming%20a%20canopy%20over%20the%20Ark%20and%20its%20carrying%20poles.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20poles%20were%20so%20long%20that%20their%20ends%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20Holy%20Place%2C%20which%20is%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Most%20Holy%20Place%2C%20but%20not%20from%20the%20outside.%20They%20are%20still%20there%20to%20this%20day.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ENothing%20was%20in%20the%20Ark%20except%20the%20two%20stone%20tablets%20that%20Moses%20had%20placed%20in%20it%20at%20Mount%20Sinai%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eat%20Horeb%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20another%20name%20for%20Sinai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20where%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20made%20a%20covenant%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20when%20they%20left%20the%20land%20of%20Egypt.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20priests%20came%20out%20of%20the%20Holy%20Place%2C%20a%20thick%20cloud%20filled%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20priests%20could%20not%20continue%20their%20service%20because%20of%20the%20cloud%2C%20for%20the%20glorious%20presence%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20filled%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESolomon%20Praises%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Solomon%20prayed%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20you%20have%20said%20that%20you%20would%20live%20in%20a%20thick%20cloud%20of%20darkness.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20I%20have%20built%20a%20glorious%20Temple%20for%20you%2C%20a%20place%20where%20you%20can%20live%20forever!%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E8%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Some%20Greek%20texts%20add%20the%20line%20%3Cem%3EIs%20this%20not%20written%20in%20the%20Book%20of%20Jashar%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20king%20turned%20around%20to%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Israel%20standing%20before%20him%20and%20gave%20this%20blessing%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BPraise%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20who%20has%20kept%20the%20promise%20he%20made%20to%20my%20father%2C%20David.%20For%20he%20told%20my%20father%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2018%3BFrom%20the%20day%20I%20brought%20my%20people%20Israel%20out%20of%20Egypt%2C%20I%20have%20never%20chosen%20a%20city%20among%20any%20of%20the%20tribes%20of%20Israel%20as%20the%20place%20where%20a%20Temple%20should%20be%20built%20to%20honor%20my%20name.%20But%20I%20have%20chosen%20David%20to%20be%20king%20over%20my%20people%20Israel.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Solomon%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20father%2C%20David%2C%20wanted%20to%20build%20this%20Temple%20to%20honor%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYou%20wanted%20to%20build%20the%20Temple%20to%20honor%20my%20name.%20Your%20intention%20is%20good%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20you%20are%20not%20the%20one%20to%20do%20it.%20One%20of%20your%20own%20sons%20will%20build%20the%20Temple%20to%20honor%20me.%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BAnd%20now%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20fulfilled%20the%20promise%20he%20made%2C%20for%20I%20have%20become%20king%20in%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20place%2C%20and%20now%20I%20sit%20on%20the%20throne%20of%20Israel%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20promised.%20I%20have%20built%20this%20Temple%20to%20honor%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20have%20prepared%20a%20place%20there%20for%20the%20Ark%2C%20which%20contains%20the%20covenant%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20made%20with%20our%20ancestors%20when%20he%20brought%20them%20out%20of%20Egypt.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESolomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prayer%20of%20Dedication%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Solomon%20stood%20before%20the%20altar%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20in%20front%20of%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Israel.%20He%20lifted%20his%20hands%20toward%20heaven%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3Eand%20he%20prayed%2C%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20there%20is%20no%20God%20like%20you%20in%20all%20of%20heaven%20above%20or%20on%20the%20earth%20below.%20You%20keep%20your%20covenant%20and%20show%20unfailing%20love%20to%20all%20who%20walk%20before%20you%20in%20wholehearted%20devotion.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_8_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%228%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20have%20kept%20your%20promise%20to%20your%20servant%20David%2C%20my%20father.%20You%20made%20that%20promise%20with%20your%20own%20mouth%2C%20and%20with%20your%20own%20hands%20you%20have%20fulfilled%20it%20today.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%